---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
title="PCB Manufacturing Products, Services & Capabilities | XingFeng PCB"
description="Explore XFPCB PCB products and services: layer-count PCBs, HDI, flexible PCB, rigid-flex PCB, aluminum PCB, PCB manufacturing, PCBA and assembly capabilities."
keywords="PCB products, PCB capabilities, 1 layer PCB, 2 layer PCB, 4 layer PCB, 6 layer PCB, 8 layer PCB, 10 layer PCB, 12 layer PCB, 14 layer PCB, 16 layer PCB, HDI PCB"
canonical="https://xfpcb.com/products/"
  cssExtra={['/css/about.css', '/css/products.css']}
>
  <main>
<!-- Page Hero -->
        <section class="products-index-hero">
            <h1>Our PCB Manufacturing Capabilities</h1>
            <p>From rapid prototyping of simple double-sided boards to the mass production of extreme-density 16-layer HDI backplanes, XingFeng PCB offers a complete spectrum of electronic circuit solutions.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Product List Grid -->
        <section class="product-list-grid">
            
            <a href="/products/1-layer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>1-Layer PCB</h2>
                <p>Ultra-low cost, high volume single-sided boards. Ideal for LED lighting (Aluminum MCPCB) and simple power supplies (FR-4/CEM-1) with extreme punching efficiency.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/2-layer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>2-Layer PCB</h2>
                <p>Fast and highly reliable double-sided boards with Plated Through Holes (PTH). Perfect for rapid prototyping, Arduino shields, and consumer gadgets.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/4-layer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>4-Layer PCB</h2>
                <p>The sweet spot for modern smart devices. Dedicated GND/VCC planes provide superior EMI shielding and easier routing for IoT gateways and smart home hubs.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/6-layer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>6-Layer PCB</h2>
                <p>Engineered for critical environments. High reliability and strict impedance control (±10%) designed for industrial PLCs, automotive electronics, and medical monitors.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/8-layer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>8-Layer PCB</h2>
                <p>Mastering High-Speed Signal Integrity. Incorporates blind/buried vias (HDI) and advanced materials for telecom switches, RF modules, and advanced motherboards.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/10-layer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>10-Layer PCB</h2>
                <p>Uncompromising IPC Class 3 reliability. Precision lamination and 100% X-ray inspection for aerospace avionics, defense systems, and high-end medical imaging (MRI/CT).</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/12-layer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>12-Layer PCB</h2>
                <p>Cutting-edge tech for 5G and Data Centers. Featuring hybrid stackups (Rogers/FR-4), advanced microvia technology, and controlled depth backdrilling for 100G+ networks.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/14-layer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>14-Layer PCB</h2>
                <p>Pushing the limits of physics. Elite manufacturing for ultra-thick backplanes (>3.0mm), managing extreme thermal dissipation for supercomputers and high-frequency radar.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/16-layer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>16-Layer PCB</h2>
                <p>The pinnacle of standard multi-layer. Mastering Any-Layer HDI and massive BGA components with dedicated 1-on-1 CAM engineering support for semiconductor test equipment.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/20-layer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>20-Layer PCB</h2>
                <p>Precision 20-Layer PCB Fabrication for High-Speed Networks. Mastering back-drilling, insertion loss minimization, and extreme registration for 400G/800G enterprise data storage and core switches.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/24-layer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>24-Layer PCB</h2>
                <p>Mission-Critical 24-Layer PCBs for Aerospace & Defense. Uncompromising IPC Class 3/3-A standards, mastering resin starvation prevention, and surviving extreme thermal cycling.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/32-layer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>32-Layer PCB</h2>
                <p>Elite 32-Layer PCB Board Maker for ATE & Supercomputing. Conquering extreme aspect ratios, massive 5000+ pin BGA fan-outs, and large-format fabrication for AI hardware.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/40-layer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>40-Layer PCB</h2>
                <p>Pushing Boundaries: 40-Layer PCB Fabrication Capabilities. The absolute limit of printed circuit board physics, engineered for quantum computing interfaces and terabit core routers.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/multilayer-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>Multilayer PCB Guide</h2>
                <p>Industry-Leading Multilayer PCB Manufacturer (4 to 40 Layers). The ultimate guide to layer counts, manufacturing processes, stackup design, and cost drivers.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/high-layer-count-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>High Layer Count PCB</h2>
                <p>Your Premier High Layer Count PCB Manufacturer. A comprehensive guide to our advanced facility, yield rate management, and global logistics for 10 to 40+ layer designs.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>


            <a href="/pcb-manufacturing/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>PCB Manufacturing Services</h2>
                <p>Custom PCB fabrication, quick turn PCB, low-cost PCB builds, mass production and engineering support for rigid, flex, HDI and specialty boards.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Services</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/pcb-manufacturing/hdi-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>HDI PCB Manufacturing</h2>
                <p>High-density interconnect PCB support for compact products, BGA fanout, microvia review and advanced routing needs.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/pcb-manufacturing/flexible-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>Flexible PCB Manufacturing</h2>
                <p>Flexible circuit fabrication for compact electronics, moving assemblies and lightweight interconnects with coverlay and bend-area review.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/pcb-manufacturing/rigid-flex-pcb/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>Rigid-Flex PCB Manufacturing</h2>
                <p>Rigid-flex PCB support for products that need fewer connectors, compact packaging and reliable board-to-board transitions.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/pcb-manufacturing/aluminum-pcbs/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>Aluminum PCB Manufacturing</h2>
                <p>Thermal management PCB fabrication for LED lighting, power modules and heat-sensitive electronic applications.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Details</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/pcb-assembly/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>PCB Assembly Services</h2>
                <p>SMT, through-hole, turnkey PCBA, component sourcing, stencil support, AOI, X-Ray and functional testing options.</p>
                <span class="view-details">View Assembly Services</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/pcba-manufacturing/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>PCBA Manufacturing</h2>
                <p>Turnkey PCBA services from PCB fabrication and component sourcing to SMT/THT assembly, AOI, X-Ray inspection, functional testing, and production shipment.</p>
                <span class="view-details">Request PCBA Quote</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/pcb-manufacturer-usa-vs-china/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>PCB Manufacturer USA vs China</h2>
                <p>A practical sourcing guide for buyers comparing pcb fabrication usa, American PCB manufacturers, China PCB manufacturing, HDI capability, cost, lead time, and compliance fit.</p>
                <span class="view-details">Read Guide</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/pcb-manufacturer-in-vietnam-vs-china/" class="product-list-item">
                <h2>PCB Manufacturer in Vietnam vs China</h2>
                <p>A China+1 sourcing guide for buyers comparing Vietnam PCB manufacturing with China PCB fabrication, multilayer capability, HDI depth, landed cost, and supplier risk.</p>
                <span class="view-details">Read Guide</span>
            </a>

        </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
